## Key Model Parameters

### Interpolation
- **Method:** Natural cubic spline
- **Boundary Condition:** Natural (second derivative = 0 at endpoints)
- **Number of Points:** 48 historical monthly observations

### Extrapolation
- **Trend Period:** Last 6 months of data
- **Trend Type:** Linear regression on daily basis
- **Seasonality Weight:** 30% of seasonal adjustment applied
- **Minimum Price Floor:** $0.50/MMBtu (below market floor)

### Storage Cost Assumption
- **Fixed Rate:** $0.50/MMBtu per month
- **Duration-Based:** Scales with days held

